      rawContext = "\tmacro_GuiSetWinVisable(\"NPCSAY\", 0)\nend\n\n\n\t\tmacro_ExecPanTaoCommand(0)\nmacro_ServerRunScript(2,3003)\nmacro_GuiSetWinVisable(\"NPCSAY\", 0)\n\n--ó´ÌÒ´ó»á\n\nmacro_GuiSetText(\"helpcontext\", \"\\n\\n#0<6>¡ô#0<5>Guild War#0<6>¡ô\\n\\n¡¡¡¡#0<0>Relevant NPC£ºCloud City£­Guild Manager\\n\\n    #0<8>¡ö Rules of War  ¡ö#0<0>\\n    ¢ÙRegistration: \\n    Only Guild Master, Vice Guild Master and Guild Counsellor can register at Guild Manager for competition. Others are forbidden. A single guild can register only once. Registration starts from 9th day each month and lasts for 3 days! The registration is invalid after the expiration date date.#0<5>Tips: #0<3>#0<0>\\n\\n    ¢ÚRequirements: \\n    16 or 32 teams are required for Guild War and it will be cancelled if the number is below requirement. ( If between 16 and 32, the first 16 will be picked out according to Guild level. If beyond 32, pick out first 32 according to the Guild level.)\\n\\n    ¢ÛAbout the war:\\n    After Guild War starts, the war will be held once each three days. (16 out of 32 will be eliminated. Then 8 out of the upgraded 16 will be eliminated and so on until one of them is champion.) Each game will be held at 19 o'clock that night. Each team will get 15 minutes to do some preparation in a mock map. After your Guild Counsellor finishes team-organizing click the \"Ready\" button. Then just wait for the convention starts.#0<8>Tips: Your team will be invalid without Guild Counsellor.#0<0>During the convention, you can use only appointed fight medicines.(You can only use the exclusive medicines made by Guild Alchemy House.).\\n\\n    ¢ÜAbout War's result: \\n    You can win if your opponents all die. If the war starts and one of opponent is not prepared, the unprepared side fails. If both sides fail to get prepared, the higher level Guild will be the winner.\\n\\n    ¢ÝPrize for winner: \\n    Huge amount of Guild materials will be rewarded to Champion and Runner-up. Individual prize will be presented like MPs and Guild contributes. And the Champion will get a extra special title.(It will go with your team until next convention.). Third, Fourth place will get abundant Guild materials as presents. Certain amount of Guild materials will be awarded to Fifth place, Sixth place, Seventh place and Eighth place.\")\n\n\nmacro_GuiSetTextCurrentP(\"helpcontext\")\nmacro_GuiSetWinVisable(\"HELPWIN\", 1)\nmacro_GuiSetWinVisable(\"NPCSAY\", 0)\nnpc_id=macro_GetSeeNpcId()\nnpc_type=macro_GetSeeNpcType()\n\niaddmax=0\ntask_addid={\n{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},\n\n}\n\niawardmax=0\ntask_awardid={\n{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},\n\n}\n\ngc_fileExec(\".\\\\script\\\\public\\\\pub_see.lua\")\n\n\nnpc_id=macro_GetNowNpcId()\nnpc_type=macro_GetNowNpcType()\nclaver=\"#0<00>¡¡¡¡My dad said we should be a useful man. Nalory is a good boy. but...\\n\\n\"\n\n\niaddmax=0\ntask_addid={\n{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},\n\n}\n\nitalkmax=0\ntask_talkid={\n{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},\n"
