ne, many envoys have already been sent to the human world, ally with them!\\nThe arrows on the ground will lead you to the Peach Garden, you'll find Apollo there near the Jade Emperor. He'll take you down to the human world. On your way you'll see many fairies, they have a lot of useful information for you. So if you're not very confident of yourself, you'd better listen to what they say.\\nFor me, I'm going to introduce the Shortcuts and give some medicines, make good use of them.\\n\"\n\n\nclaver=claver..\"\\n\\n\\n#0<2>¡¾Shortcut¡¿strategy£º#2<08><4001><0>Click and check\"\nclaver=claver..\"\\n\\n  #2<08><1000><0>¡ïGo to Human World at Apollo¡ï\"\nif(macro_IsPlayerVar(3,4)~=4)then\nclaver=claver..\"\\n\\n\\n#2<04><1001><1>Take the medicines\"\nend\n\niaddmax=1"
