      rawContext = "}\n\nstrtalk=\"¡¡¡¡This is the entrance to Peach Garden. Staff only!\\n\\n\"\nmacro_RoleSay(npc_id,1,strtalk)\n\ngc_fileExec(\".\\\\script\\\\public\\\\pub_see.lua\")\n\n\nnpc_id=macro_GetNowNpcId()\nnpc_type=macro_GetNowNpcType()\nclaver=\"#0<00>I'm very glad to see such a lively youngster like you to be an envoy of ours. As you know, the human world is suffering from a disaster. It's your duty to protect those kind people and we don't have much time to waste! Fortunately you won't fight alone, many envoys have already been sent to the human world, ally with them!\\nThe arrows on the ground will lead you to the Peach Garden, you'll find Apollo there near the Jade Emperor. He'll take you down to the human world. On your way you'll see many fairies, they have a lot of useful information for you. So if you're not very confident of yourself, you'd better listen to what they say.\\nFor me, I'm going to introduce the Shortcuts and give some medicines, make good use of them.\\n\"\n\n\nclaver=claver..\"\\n\\n\\n#0<2>¡¾Shortcut¡¿strategy£º#2<08><4001><0>Click and check\"\nclaver=claver..\"\\n\\n  #2<08><1000><0>¡ïGo to Human World at Apollo¡ï\"\nif(macro_IsPlayerVar(3,4)~=4)then\nclaver=claver..\"\\n\\n\\n#2<04><1001><1>Take the medicines\"\nend\n\niaddmax=1\ntask_addid={\n{50,\"Disgusting Darkness Sorcerer!!!\"},\n{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},\n}\n\nitalkmax=1\ntask_talkid={\n{50,1,\"¡¡¡¡According to Jade Emperor's order to pick out able man on earth for taking part in Guild Convention. You are lucky to be choosen. It's an opptunity for you to fulful your task. Jade Emperor and Goddess of Heaven are waiting for you!Come on!\",\"\\n\\n\\n\\n#2<02><25><50>I'll go!\",\"\\n#2<02><7><1>I've got something else to do.\"},\n{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},\n}\n\niawardmax=0\ntask_awardid={\n{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},\n}\n\n\n\ngc_fileExec(\".\\\\script