      },
      rawContext = "\nmacro_GuiSetText(\"NPCSAY.npcsay\", claver)\nmacro_GuiSetWinVisable(\"NPCSAY\", 1)claver=\"#0<00>¡¡¡¡It would be much easier if I knew what Rainbow Stone is. It is said that the stone has a very magic power. Anyone sees it and then makes a wish, his or her dream will come true. And the history also tells us that the Rainbow Stone belongs to the people in Celestial State. But it is only a legend, no one really knows where it is.\\n\\n\"\n\nclaver=claver..\"\\n\\n\\n#2<02><4005><0>Did God of Venus help you?\"\n\nmacro_GuiSetText(\"NPCSAY.npcsay\", claver)\nmacro_GuiSetWinVisable(\"NPCSAY\", 1)claver=\"#0<00>¡¡¡¡Several months later, I failed to bring the Stone. They breached the agreement and waged a war on us. We were not that strong, but still, we could reduce the damage at the minimu. They were unhappy about the result and sent powerful witches to strengthen their forces. We were completely defeated. A few days before, my mother had a dream that Jade Emperor would send God of Venus to help us. Actually the dream came true.\\n\\n\"\n\nclaver=claver..\"\\n\\n\\n#2<02><4006><0>Do you still love Nalan?\"\n\nmacro_GuiSetText(\"NPCSAY.npcsay\", claver)\nmacro_GuiSetWinVisable(\"NPCSAY\", 1)claver=\"#0<00>¡¡¡¡ I thought a lot and I believe She must have not a finger in this incident. The strange thing is that I never saw Nalan when we were in Nalan State. There must be some secrets. Can you help me find out?\\n\\n\"\n\n\nmacro_GuiSetText(\"NPCSAY.npcsay\", claver)\nmacro_GuiSetWinVisable(\"NPCSAY\", 1)npc_id=macro_GetSeeNpcId()\nnpc_type=macro_GetSeeNpcType()\n\niaddmax=0\ntask_addid={\n{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},\n\n}\n\niawardmax=3\ntask_awardid={\n{84,\"I'm the prince of Longicorn State, Norman.\",1},\n\n{507,\"Got that response?\",1},\n{507,\"It's all my fault~\",3},\n{788,\"Finally those monsters got killed.\",1},\n{789,\"Finally those monsters got killed.\",1},\n\n{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},\n\n}\n\ngc_fileExec(\".\\\\script\\\\public\\\\pub_see.lua\")\n\nnpc_id=macro_GetNowNpcId()\nnpc_type=macro_GetNowNpcType()\nclaver=\"#0<00>¡¡¡¡Whose child littered on the streets? Bad kid!\\n\\n\"\n\nif(macro_GetTaskStep(498)>1)then\nclaver=claver..\"\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n#0<4><Quest>£º#2<02><1001><0>Exchange \"..macro_GetItemName(20018)..\" for \"..macro_GetItemName(21269)..\"\\n\"\nend\n\niaddmax=0\ntask_addid={\n{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},{},\n\n}\n\n\nitalkmax=0"
